title.rendered: “IDF Continues Manhunt After Highway 55 Shooting Attack: Latest Updates”

content.rendered:
IDF Spokesperson:

IDF forces continue to search for the terrorist who carried out the shooting attack on Highway 55

Following the attack on Highway 55 earlier today, IDF forces continue to search for the terrorist who committed the attack.

Attached are photos from the situation assessment of the Central Command Commander, the Judea and Samaria Division Commander and the Ephraim Brigade Commander at the scene of the attack: https://idfanc.activetrail.biz/ANC070420248745963

Attached is documentation on the topic: https://bit.ly/3U7GDHA

Attached are photos from the forces’ pursuit of the terrorist: https://idfanc.activetrail.biz/ANC0704202478564
